"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"1、下载命令\\n\\n`wget https://dev.mysql.com/get/mysql57-community-release-el7-9.noarch.rpm`\\n\\n2、yun源安装命令\\n\\n`rpm -ivh mysql57-community-release-el7-9.noarch.rpm`\\n\\n3、使用yum命令安装mysql\\n\\n`yum -y install mysql-server`\\n\\n4、启动mysql\\n\\n`systemctl start mysqld`\\n\\n5、检查是否安装启动成功\\n\\n`systemctl status mysqld`\\n\\n6、查看默认密码\\n\\n`grep 'temporary password' /var/log/mysqld.log`\\n\\n7、登录修改密码\\n\\n`mysql -u root -p`\\n\\n8、修改密码\\n\\n因为5.7及以上版本的数据库对密码做了强度要求，默认密码的要求必须是大小写字母数字特殊字母的组合且至少要8位长度\\n\\n`ALTER USER 'root'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY '新的密码';`\\n\\n```sql\\nalter user user() identified by \\\"密码\\\";\\n```\\n\\n9、允许远程登录\\n\\n`GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO 'root'@'%' IDENTIFIED BY '密码' WITH GRANT OPTION;`\\n\\n10、如仍然无法访问则需关闭防火墙或者开放3306端口访问权限\\n\\n附：CentOS 7 关闭防火墙命令\\n\\n`systemctl stop firewalld.service`\\n\\n`systemctl disable firewalld.service`\\n\\n11、查看端口号\\n\\n```sql\\nshow global variables like 'port';\\n```\\n\\n12、查看防火墙状态：\\n\\n`systemctl status firewalld`\\n\\n13、开放端口放行：\\n\\n`firewall-cmd --zone=public --add-port=3306/tcp --permanent`\\n\\n加上--permanet参数永久生效，如果前面修改了端口号，此处的3306就应改成对应的端口号，然后使用命令重新读取防火墙规则：\\n\\n`firewall-cmd --reload`\\n\\n[Centos7离线安装mysql8  https://www.cnblogs.com/quchunhui/p/11115339.html](https://www.cnblogs.com/quchunhui/p/11115339.html)\\n\\n[https://www.cnblogs.com/blackmanzhang/p/11062817.html](https://www.cnblogs.com/blackmanzhang/p/11062817.html)\\n\\n[https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Cb4y1R7Er](https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Cb4y1R7Er?from=search&seid=8676128307902621472&spm_id_from=333.337.0.0)\\n\\n[https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1d54y1R7zw](https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1d54y1R7zw)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1636788883,\"title\":\"CentOs安装mysql\"},\"digest\":\"iBt8_jRzaOo_GOr7qQzuMoBA8DNkNbmONdz2q8_U_f8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xdC8F27bF5782747c336a1BEfeC1D35A20E739718\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"UtkGskyDkp0gK6mF4nIJkd6VNUz3nqq8rLJdEQnQlgA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"yhyDe8tepXn4n1N3RXVfQbqA9LQc5WLwKMuM_afrzaM\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"DsJkMBzUqcV6gda438RhCAaVRjS-F1bBphtbltjaDXzJ2T6uABQfpPwobrWk7bCcsq7_Us_nTH9ccCfTmkN67A\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xce3e13cc22f4e0303fb29a75c630aa42cfcc14da972b7c6ff2310f7436214214697e530a14b28c54638124cf1732bac87f96307bf039abb4d9b3f03ff15392f01c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"UtkGskyDkp0gK6mF4nIJkd6VNUz3nqq8rLJdEQnQlgA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"yhyDe8tepXn4n1N3RXVfQbqA9LQc5WLwKMuM_afrzaM\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"iBt8_jRzaOo_GOr7qQzuMoBA8DNkNbmONdz2q8_U_f8\"}"